<body>
    <h1>Get Eligible Arrivals</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"8f172ede16c8"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"5957b763e370"><strong>Category:</strong> Reservations</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"f1fdceb19891" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-Overview">Overview<=
/h2>
<p local-id=3D"8f4a75ff85cc">The <strong>Get Eligible Arrivals</strong> act=
ion retrieves a list of confirmed reservations arriving on a specified date=
 and determines whether each guest qualifies for special treatment. Qualifi=
cation can be based on <strong>loyalty membership</strong> (hard signals) o=
r <strong>behavioral metrics</strong> such as stay frequency, total revenue=
, and recency of last visit (soft signals). This makes it ideal for automat=
ing guest recognition workflows =E2=80=94 for example, identifying VIP gues=
ts arriving today so they can receive a room upgrade, a welcome amenity, or=
 a personalized greeting.</p>
<p local-id=3D"aa68d96764de">The component returns two output options: a de=
tailed list of reservations (including guest information, room category, ar=
rival and departure dates, and how the guest qualified) or a simple list of=
 reservation IDs that can be passed to downstream components for further pr=
ocessing.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7f94b6cf-34f3-40a0-b0d4-29f856218de1">
<h2 local-id=3D"4a6008db5675" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-InputFields">Input =
Fields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"fc0462d4-544b-479e-8970-46e=
a1c385471" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"019bdd7a-65f9-44d8-b150-87e589371f3e">
<th data-local-id=3D"a17d190c-d948-483c-8625-fc1acd8e58ca" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"47bf4c75b675">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c0c3c699-c62e-444b-bb2b-0e35dd475749" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8c0acffa06ac">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"1f519b03-c1fa-41a1-bce9-d8101944941b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bafc3857bfbd">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"281910da-a238-4c39-a7ca-f74fb33ff56a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"07755d27076a">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3c89b2f4-c2ef-4965-960e-c63aeba7a238">
<td data-local-id=3D"e7a42923-5fee-4652-bc8c-e8db745fa563" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d1d30f2bacda"><strong>Arrival Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5eccd3bb-25ac-42f0-b324-a04e2f88da9f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"52ab7cd5f0c5"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e909b894-7594-4fef-a085-4fa33f1874c3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eb79a4faccec">Date</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"88711cce-2506-443f-b2f8-85d61d2d674a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bb0e734710f6">The date to search for arriving reservations. =
Only confirmed reservations with an arrival date matching this value will b=
e returned. Format: <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"10af5149-69a8-4bda-9541-ebf135c9b311">
<td data-local-id=3D"b9781ba4-9396-4a81-af44-2c76549b6bfe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f6a1ad65d223"><strong>Loyalty Programs</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e7c7ec4-de44-4684-ab09-6b8076605456" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"43e71bddffa8"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ebc2e7e6-80c1-4c8f-b6b1-eb13613e4f16" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e9a6cdeb80b8">Multi-select</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c66d5ccc-74e2-4609-9122-f3c2c002d64a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e18375bbb615">One or more loyalty programs to filter by. Whe=
n selected, only guests who are members of the specified loyalty programs w=
ill qualify via hard signals. The dropdown is populated dynamically with th=
e loyalty programs configured in your property. This field is located in th=
e <strong>Loyalty</strong> section.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2f9ad608-1869-4303-8362-12a97ac04248">
<td data-local-id=3D"09638915-49c1-4446-acaa-6ad545b51ae0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"446d4e1a706b"><strong>Loyalty Tiers</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4c28b73d-764a-4ff5-afe4-06d1a2de22aa" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"933827afdd60"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7a21682a-5c79-405f-8dd2-9f652a19dd90" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eb41c007d750">Multi-select</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5c9900a4-6620-4cc0-b8ba-a76982caf43b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dbb25eec5c90">One or more loyalty tiers to further narrow th=
e loyalty filter. Only visible after at least one loyalty program is select=
ed. The dropdown is populated dynamically with the tiers belonging to the s=
elected programs. This field is located in the <strong>Loyalty</strong> sec=
tion.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"728311e8-23bd-475b-bbeb-bf8cdde0c211">
<td data-local-id=3D"61e28797-7dcb-4306-af74-980db70ee12b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92c82e0898ba"><strong>Stay Count Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4af34338-62fa-4a37-a8a0-6eeaf3768360" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84fd61d13d8d"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5e0f42d3-285f-42ed-88b1-4ecbc903b180" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bf50388048d6">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d7fdb66b-573e-4c54-9a0d-3a8e88b8e2f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4ecb50e6cd9a">The minimum number of past stays a guest must =
have to qualify via soft signals. For example, setting this to <code>5</cod=
e> means only guests who have stayed at least 5 times will be included thro=
ugh behavioral qualification. This field is located in the <strong>Behavior=
al signals</strong> section.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dacd1b88-b256-4fbf-aece-8f82e5b53e36">
<td data-local-id=3D"c19ecaf9-10f4-44f5-b9ca-9b8c233b44e5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5eb9d07be947"><strong>Revenue Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"291d7cf5-1b6f-4de8-ba70-cb92026c7f7d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"20816a095336"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5e7a6a01-1155-4591-adca-38922816de42" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12694e657642">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ec63665d-000e-490b-850a-a3087bc846f5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"763a105e52dd">The minimum total revenue (in the property's d=
efault currency) a guest must have generated to qualify via soft signals. R=
evenue is calculated from total payments associated with the guest's past r=
eservations. This field is located in the <strong>Behavioral signals</stron=
g> section.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"919458fc-6fa6-4c5a-90b5-398aabc467a3">
<td data-local-id=3D"00753487-b183-4838-af0f-74177badc09d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"032d905a56d6"><strong>Recency Threshold</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"129a5a51-c321-4994-a5e4-48fb642c0d36" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"218c6936152c"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"49bef84e-c590-4b14-930a-38b5bb6475f0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eb2b6519b556">Number</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e6fd3ccd-1cfa-412b-935d-c309b18edc61" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9cfb9b750833">The maximum number of days since the guest's m=
ost recent stay to qualify via soft signals. For example, setting this to <=
code>365</code> means only guests who stayed within the last year will be i=
ncluded. This field is located in the <strong>Behavioral signals</strong> s=
ection.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"12695fb7-11cc-4df7-b99f-d85e2a05a467">
<td data-local-id=3D"9543f0b6-e78f-4b9c-a9b6-db52cff40f84" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cebd3982bf5e"><strong>Rates</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18ccb6d2-64bd-4643-9692-5c5fbfe85849" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"40dbfe492494"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"565f0456-a59b-419b-8279-17d614bb12c7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0376f373246">Multi-select</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fd3f7717-c6e1-4444-9e7b-8e3befcf77d4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f4ae24d4d32a">One or more rates to filter reservations by. W=
hen selected, only reservations booked under the specified rates will be in=
cluded. The dropdown is populated dynamically with the rates configured in =
your property. This field is located in the <strong>Rates</strong> section.=
</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a5c9379618b3"><strong>Note:</strong> The <strong>Loyalty</st=
rong>, <strong>Behavioral signals</strong>, and <strong>Rates</strong> sect=
ions are collapsed by default. Expand them to access the optional filtering=
 fields.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"439786a5-4780-4b4b-84de-314063364331">
<h2 local-id=3D"b62353d5dd01" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-OutputFields">Outpu=
t Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9a4a89d44265">The component provides two output options on t=
he <strong>out</strong> port. You can choose which format to use in your wo=
rkflow:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"e83d4b130e5a" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-Option1:Reservation=
s">Option 1: Reservations</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b15a230b5665">Returns detailed reservation objects with gues=
t, room, and qualification information:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"318d91a9-b1b5-46ec-a693-49c=
dde66bbac" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"aece17ac-6809-40b7-b0c6-b5206bacad2c">
<th data-local-id=3D"fea101c5-3681-4fbb-b40c-afd87dc2d8b1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"65f986a2d94e">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"bd115ac2-613c-495c-ac85-fc3f1cd5b27a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9f3af2bfe66e">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c038183f-43c8-437e-8150-6e9b06deca80" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9b3bc0d1b5d9">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5dbc605e-50a9-4cd6-8e65-aa85621e6e9b">
<td data-local-id=3D"3c6224f6-80ac-48b5-8458-4f2204b48970" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd1f49e83136"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2e121d3d-65aa-407e-8595-a6e7bb3a4f9e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12b91eefcabf">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"80660e11-74be-44d4-bc73-29fe64514af8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"17a4533b7b25">The unique identifier of the reservation.</p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f8d08486-59ca-4ac1-a540-1ee713a1b7e4">
<td data-local-id=3D"e92f3f36-2822-448c-acf9-a51e5eeefba4" class=3D"conflue=
