<p local-id=3D"5fa8c10c4145">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fcd6a728-d456-43e2-87cb-71385177602c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0f39a1917a8">The last name of the guest.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5c4168cf-3738-48eb-a88f-f627e5b93b9f">
<td data-local-id=3D"abc6dc8b-fbba-44c0-906e-8ad1518aba70" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"da95a42015f2"><strong>Guest Email</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b9ece3fb-8a88-4f7a-a784-b7fcd55b565a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ec41fb467d19">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"81eae4b8-a96d-4f92-be43-fd1d0456a5bc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2caf946b0e99">The email address of the guest.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a15f9ffb-9bbc-45aa-88c4-cf0ca5ebd16f">
<td data-local-id=3D"1e570ac1-67a9-4d8c-a96c-a2f7deac2fb1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"453496588251"><strong>Current Category ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"91613890-106d-41d9-a5e2-6a4472f96ecd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e1c1cd0b7db2">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b26ec7e1-b85a-44b5-a268-ff4e04b8b4a9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c4b7511870b2">The unique identifier of the room category cur=
rently assigned to the reservation.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"39a7f53d-5e14-416f-b047-45a981878cd2">
<td data-local-id=3D"85d1427b-85b4-4d50-a3a4-1d29fb559ed3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"575a5434ab41"><strong>Current Category Name</strong></p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"2b45049d-bba6-4fdc-8b8f-b38e2afc0f1d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ae50b51c87b5">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c2498b1e-7058-40b2-b9ea-3301e589c5fd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f7087f73de7c">The localized name of the room category curren=
tly assigned to the reservation. Displays "Unknown" if the category name is=
 not available.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7c1ac5c1-c5e9-4aa8-9b4e-4162e5c4a8ae">
<td data-local-id=3D"4e3742bc-0786-4a53-b087-3a4f36b25235" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53e6324e87dc"><strong>Arrival Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"30d9acf8-fdea-46d5-8332-7d100136f8f7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3c452ed139c9">Date &amp; Time</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"40462e5c-cc72-43d6-92ff-3ca9cf3f4486" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f2e30e53daec">The scheduled arrival date and time in UTC (IS=
O 8601 format).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"71b7e41c-d5e3-433d-bb00-d12744e1f19e">
<td data-local-id=3D"9ccfb9fe-f604-45f9-a564-622d47c580bb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"70e14322ea88"><strong>Departure Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e050691c-9f87-4cba-9487-13d88b4364a8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02360388f9f2">Date &amp; Time</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a6f808d4-3562-421d-8e6e-b6c70cf214cb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dd6e3a365bd2">The scheduled departure date and time in UTC (=
ISO 8601 format).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3123e5f8-0238-4243-ad5b-0afcf4f791c9">
<td data-local-id=3D"4f2cff9c-8668-433d-b219-808281063ca0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ee917bf9bfc1"><strong>Qualified Via</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f92fdc2e-c351-45d3-938a-249722d6d582" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2cd50a5d5dd4">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"67580428-0311-47a1-b5f6-90f2ba883028" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"81f93fd020ed">How the guest qualified for inclusion. Values:=
 <code>hard</code> (qualified through loyalty membership) or <code>none</co=
de> (no loyalty match =E2=80=94 qualified through soft signals or no loyalt=
y filtering was applied).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"95c5d526-be57-4ab2-9c35-584640194879">
<td data-local-id=3D"5f20dc47-6d88-44b7-a643-10ebe72ade9b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1f9622103d2"><strong>Loyalty Tier Name</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"55fbe5fb-5976-43f8-9bc5-69a28bb5ed92" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b389c8018e4d">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9e32b841-46f2-4f97-bbd4-622ad470ce23" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"431bf27dd6fd">The name of the guest's loyalty tier, if appli=
cable. Empty when the guest does not have a matching loyalty membership.</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e31fefbc-4906-4bd6-99fb-ac992ee88c44">
<td data-local-id=3D"561ad8da-de57-47dd-bfff-278089148761" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0bc039db050c"><strong>Loyalty Program Name</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1a441a03-44eb-495a-a1b2-fd2480c7d42d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb14ad260150">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d3f30770-44e9-442e-9169-9d156c068731" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9205e99864f1">The name of the guest's loyalty program, if ap=
plicable. Empty when the guest does not have a matching loyalty membership.=
</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"4c230bd1a681" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-Option2:Reservation=
IDs">Option 2: Reservation IDs</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c92a467988fa">Returns a simple array of reservation ID strin=
gs. This is useful when you only need the IDs to pass to another component =
(e.g., a Room Upgrade action) without the additional guest and room details=
.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"88ef3998-50a0-435c-b8b7-9157a595a5a7">
<h2 local-id=3D"9e98c74204ef" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-HowItWorks">How It =
Works</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ecc42217-ccd4-43ae-82d7-83879c21d5b2">
<li local-id=3D"f89039f5-a4ac-4a5b-a20b-0e1da4bef686">
<p local-id=3D"bc0a106662e0">The component receives the <strong>Arrival Dat=
e</strong> and any optional filters from the previous step or from manually=
 configured values.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"edc5e637-3240-40ac-a1fa-ccf419f3d523">
<p local-id=3D"f5d8e87efcf4">It fetches all <strong>confirmed reservations<=
/strong> arriving on the specified date that have an assigned room. Reserva=
tions without a room assignment are excluded.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee3934f5-2cfd-4452-820c-3388c5675875">
<p local-id=3D"1b2fc3812e7a">If <strong>Loyalty Programs</strong> or <stron=
g>Loyalty Tiers</strong> are specified, reservations are filtered to only i=
nclude guests with an active membership in those programs or tiers. These g=
uests are marked as qualified via <strong>hard signals</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e75071a3-4746-4fd4-8a06-979c3451b992">
<p local-id=3D"37a4ea48f0f6">If any <strong>Behavioral signal thresholds</s=
trong> (Stay Count, Revenue, or Recency) are configured, guests who did <em=
>not</em> qualify through loyalty are evaluated against these thresholds. A=
 guest must meet <strong>all</strong> specified thresholds to qualify via <=
strong>soft signals</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d7573a7-8891-49d5-b22c-36c22b272519">
<p local-id=3D"a8490bfac913">If <strong>Rates</strong> are specified, only =
reservations booked under those rates are included.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"460d5b9e-4e67-48f5-b532-3673ce78bd60">
<p local-id=3D"d2443b81d34c">Results are sorted by <strong>loyalty tier ran=
k</strong> (highest tier first), then by reservation creation date, then by=
 guest account creation date.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6fef429-7d69-4ddb-b550-e3801dc00f44">
<p local-id=3D"95571c01c41b">The final list is returned with full reservati=
on details on the <strong>Reservations</strong> output or as a list of IDs =
on the <strong>Reservation IDs</strong> output.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"6430eb12-55d1-42bf-8ebb-272d6e6cc70b">
<h2 local-id=3D"f08980149679" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-HardSignalsvs.SoftS=
ignals">Hard Signals vs. Soft Signals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0359388582a9">The component uses a two-tier qualification sy=
stem to identify eligible guests:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"ffaeb15f-c1c3-4b73-8680-f46=
2f119d2a0" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"014ea6d0-da94-4474-ae7b-3e4c6e78e785">
<th data-local-id=3D"7026959e-02f5-4b98-a6df-cfae51a3e4ba" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7cb549651110">Signal Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"53360ea0-11aa-48bd-8512-0debaf4c624f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b9b586cbd8d0">Based On</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"51e80f72-ad46-43ba-af33-53a44733991a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a8cbb149456e">How It Works</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5db87aa5-1519-4bc0-a791-f065ee09e3f6">
<td data-local-id=3D"16c4d3ac-85c9-4e5d-a152-ef7c4e445840" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5686cc2fd704"><strong>Hard signals</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b5c97e65-ec11-47cc-b7d1-a1571fdfead6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0f41dd215203">Loyalty membership</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"45a5663f-2fc3-4d9d-877e-0ff9d5c847c6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"84f6d80104cd">Guests who are members of the selected loyalty=
 programs and/or tiers automatically qualify. They are evaluated first and =
marked with <code>qualifiedVia =3D "hard"</code>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d0140942-53d0-451c-b8f5-d68a1895234b">
<td data-local-id=3D"ef382c09-ca14-495e-9b07-74a4b894a1a9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5f329c941a96"><strong>Soft signals</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8c94fa63-74a8-410d-88bc-abc91de1c108" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4580b27cdcd7">Behavioral metrics</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"81ac609a-d07d-4fa5-bf97-b5ec0f67acf8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"170a9129cd93">Guests who did <em>not</em> qualify through lo=
yalty are evaluated based on their stay history, total revenue, and recency=
. They must meet <strong>all</strong> configured thresholds to qualify. Sof=
t signal evaluation only runs when at least one threshold is set.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6a65b4905c39"><strong>Note:</strong> If no loyalty programs,=
 tiers, or behavioral thresholds are configured, <strong>all</strong> confi=
rmed reservations with a room assignment arriving on the specified date are=
 returned. The qualification field will show <code>none</code> for all gues=
ts.</p>
<p local-id=3D"637f2cd3b6e0"><strong>Important:</strong> Soft signal thresh=
olds work with an AND logic =E2=80=94 if you set both a Stay Count Threshol=
d of <code>5</code> and a Revenue Threshold of <code>1000</code>, a guest m=
ust have at least 5 stays <strong>and</strong> at least 1000 in total reven=
ue to qualify. If any single threshold is not met, the guest is excluded.</=
p>
<hr local-id=3D"6d24d64c-6806-4331-855e-dca635350256">
<h2 local-id=3D"223e6cf256cf" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-ExampleUseCases">Ex=
ample Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ea3b53aa-356d-4ccd-b117-6ac170cbaf16">
<li local-id=3D"9987e168-01de-4174-86ab-a30f38728482">
<p local-id=3D"a153c0545f5e"><strong>VIP room upgrade workflow</strong> =E2=
=80=94 Retrieve today's arrivals filtered by a "Gold" or "Platinum" loyalty=
 tier, then pass the reservation IDs to a Room Upgrade component to automat=
ically offer upgrades to top-tier guests.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b89b267-eac6-42cd-b3df-e632b97664c8">
<p local-id=3D"293e4204f1e4"><strong>Loyalty guest welcome amenity</strong>=
 =E2=80=94 Fetch arriving guests who belong to any loyalty program, then cr=
eate a task for the front desk to prepare a personalized welcome package fo=
r each loyalty guest.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e17234d-59be-4696-ad1f-bb0424cb2049">
<p local-id=3D"f7a869af37e6"><strong>High-value guest recognition</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Use behavioral thresholds (e.g., at least 10 stays and 5,000 in t=
otal revenue) to identify frequent high-spending guests who may not be in a=
 formal loyalty program, and send a notification to the front office manage=
r.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a8af413d-d866-4b1b-b847-600b1d3038df">
<p local-id=3D"f2aba4d511bc"><strong>Rate-specific arrival list</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Filter arrivals by a specific promotional rate to generate a dail=
y list of guests who booked through a special offer, enabling targeted foll=
ow-up or upselling.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85eeaeb1-2b97-4bfa-90b4-96487674346f">
<p local-id=3D"833d68a1657b"><strong>Combined loyalty and behavioral filter=
ing</strong> =E2=80=94 Select a loyalty program to capture formal members, =
and also set a recency threshold of 180 days to additionally include recent=
 repeat guests, ensuring no high-value arrival is overlooked.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6e8ba053-d574-41b7-b4d5-5d3ba763cac5">
<h2 local-id=3D"fad5418fec73" id=3D"GetEligibleArrivals-Sorting">Sorting</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"62617f2ac720">The returned reservations are sorted in the fo=
llowing order:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"0c3e238e-a5ad-4160-8da4-f9b073c6ebe3">
<li local-id=3D"1fb06825-b022-4f79-9de9-d29d22991142">
<p local-id=3D"79ef65c69aa9"><strong>Loyalty tier rank</strong> (descending=
) =E2=80=94 Guests in higher-ranked loyalty tiers appear first.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a67c115a-f516-4e8e-bf92-2bf929a833a6">
<p local-id=3D"575219ab00ee"><strong>Reservation creation date</strong> (de=
scending) =E2=80=94 Among guests with the same tier rank (or no tier), more=
 recently created reservations appear first.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fad19af5-3832-42b4-bb3d-c2cda2ae0af6">
<p local-id=3D"a17aeb21e466"><strong>Guest account creation date</strong> (=
descending) =E2=80=94 If reservations share the same creation date, newer g=
uest accounts appear first.</p></li>
</ol>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
